There is no better way to prepare for the LSAT than practicing the official test questions. This practice package contains all the questions asked in the June 2012 LSAT examinations. Licensed directly from LSAC (the official administrator of the LSAT exams), the test is conveniently packaged in this app. The app allows you to practice the test interactively.
